claim: Flublok contains 3x the hemagglutinin (HA) antigen content of standard-dose flu vaccines, which has been linked to greater immunogenicity vs standard-dose flu vaccines.
explanation: Journal header page showing the Vaccine journal title, Elsevier logo, ScienceDirect link, and journal homepage URL does not support the claim because the image contains only the journal title and publisher information with no data on Flublok antigen content or immunogenicity Note: None
